__e: Oh, believe me, next time I will. I couldn't help overhearing. You two are talking about the new hoIonoveI.
We regret that we forced Commander Chakotay to assist us, but it was necessary for our survival.
I had only one agenda with you, Chakotay, and I never kept it secret.
It doesn't make sense, unless it's Chakotay and he knows we'll be in danger.
Although Commander Chakotay and I won't be with you for the rest of your journey, we know that you'll be the same steadfast crew for Mr. Tuvok as you have been for us.
